cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper deals with image privacy prediction using deep features, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the use of deep learning techniques and neural networks is also relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The potential privacy violations that can occur on social media sites also fall under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and the use of machine learning models for prediction can be considered a form of artificial intelligence (cs.SI).
